      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td data-en="In general, how would you rate your satisfaction with your social activities and relationships?" data-ar="بشكل عام، كيف يمكنك تقييم رضائك عن نشاطاتكاإلجتماعية وعالقاتك؟">In general, how would you rate your satisfaction with your social activities and relationships?</td>
        <td><input type="radio" name="In general, how would you rate your satisfaction with your social activities and relationships?" value="5" required></td>
        <td><input type="radio" name="In general, how would you rate your satisfaction with your social activities and relationships?" value="4"></td>
